commits.content:
name: Lint

on:
  push:
    branches: [ main, develop ]
  pull_request:
    branches: [ main, develop ]

jobs:
  lint:
    name: Lint
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    
    steps:
      - name: Checkout code
        uses: actions/checkout@v4

      - name: Enable Corepack
        run: corepack enable

      - name: Setup Node.js and dependencies
        uses: ./.github/actions/setup
        
      - name: Run ESLint
        run: yarn lint
        
      - name: Check TypeScript compilation
        run: yarn build
